35
00:02:06,526 --> 00:02:10,292
Besides, the question isn't how he knows,
but if he's right.

36
00:02:11,631 --> 00:02:13,360
TRU: And if he is...

37
00:02:15,101 --> 00:02:17,501
what am l going to find out next?

38
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,707
[Theme music]

39
00:02:34,220 --> 00:02:35,209
Help me.

40
00:02:54,607 --> 00:02:55,904
[Stomping]

41
00:02:58,178 --> 00:03:01,579
DAVlS: There's this new technology
