with you. Should l worry?

157
00:09:38,210 --> 00:09:39,336
Call me.

158
00:09:40,379 --> 00:09:41,368
<i>Thanks.</i>

159
00:09:42,715 --> 00:09:44,910
[Jazzy instrumental music playing]

160
00:09:45,885 --> 00:09:49,412
